headline: New Area 1 security study shows that U.S. State & local election administrators remain vulnerable to phish
keywords: Email Security, Cloudflare Area 1, Elections, Phishing
description: With only 100 days until Election Day, Area 1 Security’s new “Phishing Election Administrators” report assesses the depth of current email security controls used by 10,000 U.S. state and local election administrators.
